    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name><ptr target="med.00764_n1"/>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <name type="place">U S America</name>
                    <date when="1884-05-28">May 28 '84</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>As far as I understand your request I cheerfully agree
                to it&#8212;As far as I have power to do so I hereby grant you the right of setting
                my poem of the <hi rend="italic">Death Carol</hi> to music &amp; copyrighting the
                music accompanied by the words, in America.<ptr target="med.00764_n2"/> </p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed> 
            </closer>
        </body>
